* Directory contents

  This folder contains Oblong's Android apps using Jelly.

  - core: shared code, in the form of an android library. You don't
    need to compile it individually.
  - ponder: a pond, i mean, pool monitor.

* App build instructions

*** Using Ant to build apps

    You'll need ant 1.6 or better.

    In each application folder you want to create, a file called
    local.properities must be created, containing the location of
    your android installation directory; e.g.

       sdk.dir=/home/jao/lib/java/android-sdk-linux_86

    That's it. Use ant

